215
00:11:59,490 --> 00:12:00,490
Jeez, Fu.

216
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:03,490
It's our family gathering, after all.

217
00:12:04,010 --> 00:12:04,900
Besides,

218
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,010
