220
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:11,920
Ready, eldest son-in-law?

221
00:12:16,530 --> 00:12:17,000
Let's go.

222
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:19,700
Papa, Mama, your Tee is here!

223
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:21,340
Let's go.

224
00:12:30,010 --> 00:12:31,590
Mama!

225
00:12:31,770 --> 00:12:32,790
While you were gone,

226
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,600
I missed you so, so much!

227
00:12:37,750 --> 00:12:39,200
I hope that was true.

228
00:12:39,340 --> 00:12:41,890
You weren't just going out
and neglecting school,

229
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:42,870
