231
00:12:45,730 --> 00:12:46,680
There!

232
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:50,440
What about you, Tai?
How have you been?

233
00:12:50,530 --> 00:12:51,580
Has school been intense?

234
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:53,290
Well, it's going okay.

235
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:57,070
