259
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:48,470
I also believe our service

260
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:50,970
will provide a good experience for our guests.

261
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:53,020
Therefore, we can set our ADR

262
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:54,550
