263
00:13:56,950 --> 00:13:58,270
What is ADR?

264
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:03,120
It's basically the room rate.

265
00:14:03,730 --> 00:14:05,390
Papa, you don't have
to worry about the hotel.

266
00:14:06,170 --> 00:14:07,100
Today,

267
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:08,790
