268
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:10,680
Let's have a nice moment, shall we?

269
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:12,990
We don't get to see
each other very often, right, Papa?

270
00:14:13,470 --> 00:14:14,080
Right, everyone?
Mm.

271
00:14:15,170 --> 00:14:15,980
That's right, dear.

272
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,980
Alright, if anyone
wants anything else to eat,

273
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:20,290
